",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 服务状态巡检\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: 服务状态巡检\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774648890834,\n      \"sessionId\": \"ab7a4392-3b2d-4e43-9b8f-b62ff6f8559b\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 45081,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/ab7a4392-3b2d-4e43-9b8f-b62ff6f8559b.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"aborted\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774648891358,\n          \"errorMessage\": \"Request was aborted.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"count":2,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1774649029691,"sessionId":"383a54ae-5fe5-4a4e-a284-438c90f7809d","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":44826,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/383a54ae-5fe5-4a4e-a284-438c90f7809d.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个定时任务（cron job），需要我：\n1. 先查询 sessions_list 检查是否有活跃对话\n2. 如果没有活跃对话，执行自主学习任务\n3. 如果有活跃对话，回复\"检测到活跃对话，不执行自主学习\"\n\n让我先查询 sessions_list。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q737lsl7rv6r_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774649030492}]},{"key":"agent:main:cron:99dd3c6e-f440-4ce5-a3aa-579918ee1